---
title: Moroccan Spiced Beef Stew with charred courgette, couscous and Greek style cheese
description: Gently charred courgette, salty Greek style cheese and a thick tomato-y beef stew sit atop a bed of fluffy couscous in this warm and hearty Middle Eastern inspired dish.
